<div id="hotspotminingContent-443043" class="hotspotminingContent clearfix showPic" style="display: block">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=472f163d67ad281af4e450bd&lemmaId=127359&lemmaId=127359&fr=qingtian" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=40fbc3da0455b3199cacd1352594b110/4034970a304e251f7af26b23a986c9177e3e53e0.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=472f163d67ad281af4e450bd&lemmaId=127359&lemmaId=127359&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">王安石：德如壁立千仞，才如汪洋恣肆，终究是大忠还是大奸？</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2019-08-14 18:08</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>越研究王安石就越被王荆公的才华和品质所折服，王安石是一名斗士，为了国家的未来甘冒矢石，政敌对他的诋毁，后世对他的误解，都无法丝毫降低王安石伟大的形象。千年以后，或许只有王安石自己的一句诗歌才能概括出他波澜壮阔的一生：心如宝月映琉璃。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=472f163d67ad281af4e450bd&lemmaId=127359&lemmaId=127359&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
